Package org.soulwing.prospecto.api.template

Class AbstractViewNodeVisitor

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.soulwing.prospecto.api.template.AbstractViewNodeVisitor
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    ViewNodeVisitor
    public abstract class AbstractViewNodeVisitor
extends Object
implements ViewNodeVisitor
    An abstract base for a ViewNodeVisitor implementation.

    This type can be subclassed to implement a ViewNodeVisitor. It provides default implementations of the interface methods that do nothing aside from returning the provided state.

    Author:
    Carl Harris
